{"word":"ἅπαξ","slug":"ἅπαξ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἅπαξ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἅπας\">ἅπας</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b><i>once</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as numerical term <b><a href='B:540 11:25'>2 Cor 11:25</a>; <a href='B:650 9:26-28'>Hb 9:26-28</a>; <a href='B:670 3:18'>1 Pt 3:18</a>,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> component of decisive aspect, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> b below; <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔτι\">ἔτι</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἅπαξ\">ἅπαξ</a></el> <i>once more</i> <b><a href='B:650 12:26'>Hb 12:26f</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἅπαξ\">ἅπαξ</a> τοῦ ἐνιαύτου</el> <i>once a year</i> <b>9:7;</b> <el>ϰαὶ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἅπαξ\">ἅπαξ</a> ϰαὶ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δίς\">δίς</a></el> <i>both once and a second</i> <i>time</i> = <i>not only once, but twice</i><b> <a href='B:570 4:16'>Phil 4:16</a>; <a href='B:590 2:18'>1 Th 2:18</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as unique and decisive occurrence <i>once (for all)</i><b> <a href='B:650 6:4'>Hb 6:4</a>; <a href='B:650 10:2'>10:2</a>; <a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 3</a>, <a href='B:720 5:1'>5</a>.</b> S. also <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐφάπαξ\">ἐφάπαξ</a></el>. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπάντησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπαράβατος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}